4. Loren Cain

# Loren Cain

## Project Coordinator Center Operations & Administration

Phone: **512-475-9411** |
Email: **[lcain@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:lcain@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Loren Cain joined the TACC team in the Center Programs group as a Project Coordinator. She is responsible for project planning, budgeting, communications, personnel resourcing, tracking and reporting. She previously held a senior research coordinator position at Dell Medical School in the departments of Women's Health and Medical Education. Loren came to Austin from Pennington Biomedical Research Center's Reproductive Endocrinology and Women's Health Laboratory in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. She studied kinesiology at Louisiana State University earning undergraduate and graduate degrees.